
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 05 of Thoracic CT
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Mass' from the dropdown menu
And I select 'I describe' radio button
When I click on 'Characterization II' tab
Then 'Pleural finger' checkbox is enabled
And 'Corona radiata/spiculae' checkbox is enabled
And 'Halo sign' checkbox is enabled
And 'Associated atelectasis' checkbox is enabled

And 'Pleura' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pericardium' checkbox is enabled

And 'Rib' checkbox is enabledAnd 'Fat' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sternum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Clavicule' checkbox is enabled
And 'Vertebral body' checkbox is enabled

And 'A. pulmonalis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Vv. pulmonary' checkbox is enabled
And 'A. subclavia' checkbox is enabled
And 'V. subclavia' checkbox is enabled

And 'Trachea' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bifurcation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Main bronchus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Plexus cervicalis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Plexus brachialis' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'A. pulmonalis' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Vv. pulmonary' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'A. subclavia' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'V. subclavia' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Main bronchus' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Plexus cervicalis' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Plexus brachialis' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
